inclusion.criterion: Ability to speak, read, and understand English
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: Documented diagnosis of migraine aura (MA) for a ≥2 year period preceding enrollment
inclusion.label: met
inclusion.evidence: confirmed by a neurology healthcare provider

inclusion.criterion: Average of 4 to 14 migraine days per month for the 3-month period preceding enrollment
inclusion.label: met

inclusion.criterion: Migraine prevention regimen stable for at least 30 days prior to enrollment
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: Documented right-to-left shunt (RLS) with 11 to 100 ET at rest or following calibrated or uncalibrated respiratory strain by TCD
exclusion.label: not_met

exclusion.criterion: History of stroke or neurological condition associated with cognitive dysfunction such as multiple sclerosis, epilepsy, brain tumor or brain injury
exclusion.label: unknown
